- Classification map can be consumed by gap-heatmap tooling without manual transforms.
- New tests failing classification are surfaced as actionable audit items.","notes":"Treat this as the source of truth for realism metrics in reporting and CI policy discussions.","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:37:51.255167215Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T00:55:12.193601731Z","closed_at":"2026-02-13T00:55:12.193582845Z","close_reason":"Realism tier classification complete in docs/test-realism/test_inventory.csv. Tiers: unit(26537), e2e(3585), in-memory(681), file-backed(232), mocked(76).","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.1.2.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.1.2","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:37:51.255167215Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-mblr.1.2.2","depends_on_id":"bd-mblr.1.2.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-12T23:38:30.579516418Z","created_by":"ubuntu","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
